These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, police-officer, freelancer, scientist
House: cape-cod, palace, futuristic, tower
1. the palace house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
2. the mechanic is the tower house##1
3. the futuristic house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
4. the police-officer is on the left of the tower house##1
5. the scientist is on the left of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Job          | scientist | freelancer | police-officer | mechanic   |
| House   | palace  | cape-cod     | futuristic   | tower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, punk, gospel, dubstep
4 different games are played: chess, canasta, poker, scrabble
1. the fan of dubstep is the person playing canasta##1
2. the fan of metal is on the far right##1
3. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the person playing poker##1
5. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | dubstep | punk | metal    |
| Game   | poker    | canasta      | chess | scrabble |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, polish, chinese, american
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, train, bike, motorbike
1. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the mexican is the person driving the boat##1
3. the person driving the train is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the american##1
5. the chinese is on the left of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Nationality         | mexican | american | chinese   | polish |
| Transport   | boat   | bike | motorbike | train         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, poker, canasta, domino
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, polish, spanish, turkish
1. the polish is the person playing domino##1
2. the person playing poker is on the left of the spanish##1
3. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
4. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing domino##1
5. the nigerian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Game   | domino | poker | scrabble  | canasta      |
| Nationality         | polish | turkish   | spanish | nigerian |

