.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, water, lemonade, mirinda
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, subway, taxi, ship
1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | lemonade | water | coffee |
| Transport    | airplane       | ship | taxi | subway     |

