.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
4 different games are played: chess, canasta, mah-jongg, poker
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, asparagus, apricot, artichoke
1. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1
2. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
4. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Game   | poker | mah-jongg | chess | canasta |
| Food           | pumpkin      | apricot | artichoke | asparagus    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
House: art-deco, palace, futuristic, cottage
4 different games are played: poker, chess, canasta, go
1. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1
2. the cottage house is on the far right##1
3. the futuristic house is on the far left##1
4. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
5. the palace house is on the left of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| House   | futuristic | palace | art-deco | cottage  |
| Game           | canasta | poker | go       | chess |

