.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, rock, gospel, salsa
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, cain, aristoff, oliveros
1. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the fan of rock##1
2. the oliveros-smoker is the fan of salsa##1
3. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of folk##1
4. the fan of gospel is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
5. the dannemann-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Music-Genre         | gospel | folk      | rock | salsa |
| Cigar   | dannemann          | cain | aristoff     | oliveros    |

