.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, aconite, rose, daffodil
House: farmhouse, art-deco, futuristic, townhouse
1. the townhouse house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
2. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far right##1
4. the art-deco house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
5. the townhouse house is on the right of the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Flower   | aconite    | rose       | dahlia | daffodil   |
| House     | art-deco | futuristic | townhouse   | farmhouse |

