.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
City: san-francisco, marseilles, colone, boston
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, june, may, july
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
2. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| City    | san-francisco | colone  | marseilles | boston |
| Birthday   | july | may | june          | february    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, dancing, chess, baking
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, green, amber, blood-red
1. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
2. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person who likes amber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Hobby      | chess | dancing  | traveling | baking |
| Color   | light-blue  | amber | blood-red           | green   |

