.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-12::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, skiing, tennis, golf
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, broccoli, cranberry, nectarine
1. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Sport   | skiing | baseball | golf | tennis  |
| Food           | nectarine | broccoli      | cranberry | pineapple |

