.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, iris, bellflower, zinnia
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, snowboarding, swimming, surfing
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
3. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
4. the person who growszinnia is the person who's sport is surfing##1
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who growsiris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Flower   | aconite | bellflower | iris | zinnia   |
| Sport     | swimming  | skateboarding    | snowboarding       | surfing |

 